      <h2>Why Support Matters</h2>

      <p>The Traveling Times is an independent creative journal — no ads, no sponsors, no paywalls. Everything published here is free to read. Your support helps keep it that way and makes it possible to keep creating new content about travel, poetry, art, fashion, music, dance, and entertainment.</p>

      <h2>How You Can Help</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Share an article</strong> — If something you read here resonates with you, share it with a friend or on social media. Word of mouth is the best kind of support.</li>
        <li><strong>Write a letter</strong> — Have thoughts on something you read? <a href="/submit/">Submit a letter</a> to the editor. Reader voices make this journal better.</li>
        <li><strong>Subscribe to the newsletter</strong> — Stay in the loop by <a href="/newsletter/">signing up for the newsletter</a>. It's free and you can unsubscribe anytime.</li>
        <li><strong>Send feedback</strong> — Ideas, suggestions, or just a kind word? Reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@thetravelingtimes.com">hello@thetravelingtimes.com</a>.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Thank You</h2>

      <p>Every reader matters. Whether you've been here since Edition 1 or you just found this site today — thank you for being part of The Traveling Times.</p>

